<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_de171506-90a0-4f7d-af12-b16c0f33181f" outputclass="ncc-clause"><sptc>C1P1</sptc><title id="_96bb0364-f3e0-43ea-a024-c2243fe57b5c">Disposal</title><archive-num>2019: CP1.1</archive-num><subclause id="_3d26fdd1-a5ee-4b74-9fd4-2fbdde47696b" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_4c8a40e5-fb55-45d4-b15c-373e82539bfe">SubClause</title><num/><p>Sewage and sullage must be conveyed through a sanitary <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1401_0.7.0.xml#_a318c0f3-5635-4ac0-b103-59d798c9f23d" id="_e3f7da8f-ddd7-4025-8ea9-12a27276cebc" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">plumbing</xref> system to—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_e2f726b5-0368-4548-8a68-407bca40f9a0">a sanitary <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1249_0.8.0.xml#_25307451-c7e1-4167-b4de-e5a1af26694c" id="_01292e10-0320-49b4-91a3-587772e84b27" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">drainage</xref> system; or</li><li id="_9e1b59d6-07d8-4f85-9b6b-7a1457a6c9d3">an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1193_0.6.0.xml#_9d2e065b-aa41-45f9-b2f5-4628d8fa28d0" id="_f7877c79-f2cd-48ef-b8ba-4e00dc54e215" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">approved disposal system</xref> authorised by an authority having jurisdiction.</li></ol></subclause><callout id="_e21ca3a3-4fae-4ba4-886a-691cc7a615db"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><p>An <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1193_0.6.0.xml#_9d2e065b-aa41-45f9-b2f5-4628d8fa28d0" id="_bedf0158-1a8e-41fb-a3b0-61c7918b9816" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">approved disposal system</xref> may be—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_b166e83f-a12b-4654-b2fb-b2d71d787b88">an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1383_4.5.0.xml#_2396187d-8435-4f01-9dfd-613970a74823" id="_6514688d-b9f1-40bf-a79c-bfba9ea1ad01" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">on-site wastewater management system</xref>; or</li><li id="_3d649c80-8ae0-48e4-bd07-3b924f4c503d">a connection to a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1376_4.2.0.xml#_12d6153c-4986-4856-80c0-e21bb57af12f" id="_05bfbc3a-6a22-47cf-b011-2fb0deadf296" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Network Utility Operator's</xref> sewerage system.</li></ol></callout><callout id="_39c29d68-e3ab-45ea-94af-80536c163f85"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><title id="_b2f70abc-b387-498c-8555-2827257e095c">Non-flushing (waterless) urinals</title><p>Where a non-flushing (waterless) urinal is to be installed to a sanitary <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1401_0.7.0.xml#_a318c0f3-5635-4ac0-b103-59d798c9f23d" id="_3e1b5444-5fb4-43b0-ab7d-cbf44256f02d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">plumbing</xref> system comprising of copper, copper alloy or other metallic piping, undiluted discharge transported through such pipework may increase the likelihood of corrosion.</p><p>Practitioners should also be aware that undiluted discharge, transported through pipework of any material, can cause a build-up of struvite (ammonium magnesium phosphate) inside the pipework, potentially causing <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1209_1.2.0.xml#_417d94d8-f254-4788-9a14-c4c5da89daa6" id="_098568a0-4fa7-4077-b195-654a772d70f8" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">blockage</xref> within the sanitary <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1401_0.7.0.xml#_a318c0f3-5635-4ac0-b103-59d798c9f23d" id="_3d0bb389-77a4-4dab-a384-c9dfe900c95d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">plumbing</xref> system.</p></callout></clause>